cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for sentiment classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of embeddings and machine learning algorithms, which are common in sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves text classification, which is relevant to sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) where text is often used as input to image or video classification tasks.
